00:03:11.330 --> 00:03:15.730
And so my question is, how is
it that a population of bipedal

00:03:15.730 --> 00:03:18.230
apes-- you know, they're not
very impressive looking, right?

00:03:18.230 --> 00:03:20.360
Kind of like we aren't, right?

00:03:20.360 --> 00:03:21.900
We don't have big weapons.

00:03:21.900 --> 00:03:23.540
We don't have antlers or horns.

00:03:23.540 --> 00:03:24.720
We don't have big teeth.

00:03:24.720 --> 00:03:30.500
We don't have this sort
