00:03:44.810 --> 00:03:49.970
bipedal apes-- and have grown
to a size of 7 billion souls

00:03:49.970 --> 00:03:54.530
in, as I say less than
1.8 million years?

00:03:54.530 --> 00:03:58.060
And we've colonized and
come to dominate nearly

00:03:58.060 --> 00:03:59.755
every terrestrial biomome.

00:03:59.755 --> 00:04:03.430
This is just a picture of making
